Author: RatEnabler
Text: I'm so sorry, Ive been there too. The worst part is when you don't even want to eat the food or enjoy it, your body is just crying out to eat something and doesn't care what it is. Try to be kinder to yourself, it's not the end of the world even if it feels like it is, you can try again tomorrow and you will only gain water weight and bloat thatll go in under a week :) x
